data.description: Beautiful newer home in quiet neighborhood, conveniently located near schools, parks, and Ft. Carson. Home has several upgrades throughout, including stainless steel appliances, extended concrete patio, walk-in closets in every bedroom, light fixtures, and central A/C for those hot Summer days! Upstairs has open loft that could be converted into a 4th bedroom. A kitchen island, lawn sprinkler system, office/living room space, walk-in kitchen pantry, and washer and dryer complete this wonderful home. Come and see it today!
